到排期日搞埋另一隻耳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c04cede8cd3a8f8eb49de1f447375dbf0a6114","tid":216051,"uid":22613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T01:23:09.000Z","msg":"旺角黃x琪"},{"pid":"5fea82913a591cff6adc6e9126f8d72f48893e0a","tid":216051,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T01:26:07.000Z","msg":"我塞過兩次，第一次去吸，第二次唔理佢過兩日通咗，不過有痛就睇醫生好啲"},{"pid":"294afccefc9dac85a634c1d3222dc0e24425e4b5","tid":216051,"uid":57952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T01:28:29.000Z","msg":"黃文琪 540蚊左右"},{"pid":"ca251962636c2947786d729daa267ac42a5b9af7","tid":216051,"uid":34845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T01:28:35.000Z","msg":"旺角黃文琪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前隻耳塞左又痛，都係佢幫我搞番掂，而且唔算貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a576a68f3b24695975af6e20294d06bfe5d30fc","tid":216051,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T01:30:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黃文琪 540蚊左右</blockquote><br />\n我近排搞一隻耳4舊水"},{"pid":"75090f33e5714a02a091d727b1bfa89e97a7d740","tid":216051,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T01:46:29.000Z","msg":"可能係外耳炎<br />\n是但搵間診所睇應該都得<br />\n但如果突然間痛犀利咗就最好即刻去急診"},{"pid":"84da55cd6dc1acef29a313f9dfd549c13292ba2a","tid":216051,"uid":94570,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T02:06:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>谷d 精上腦通返<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/BNOacD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FBNOacD.jpg&h=fe383882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/kOPKJH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FkOPKJH.jpg&h=4dfab753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/vkY8xr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.